desc: At Canoe2 you can buy SUP Boards and accessories for quick UK delivery. Established in 2010, Canoe2 are the experts in canoe hire, and short break canoe trips on the river nene in Northamptonshire, and now the perfect place to buy your Jobe SUP boards.

layout.text: Jobe SUP Specialist in Northamptonshire. Buy Instore or Online. 12 years of paddle-sport hire & sale. Trusted by novices and regular paddlers alike, highest levels of service. All delivered to you when you buy from Canoe2.
